        <abstract>
            <p>Fossil leaves from Disko Island.</p>
            <p>JDH to begin working out the botanical geography of the polar sea.</p>
            <p>Has not forgotten CD’s request on aberrant species.</p>
            <p>Has taken a house on Richmond Hill.</p>
